headline: 1 Ultra-High-Yield Dividend Stock (I Just Bought) That You Can Buy and Hold for a Decade
summary: Mr. Market, a construct of the famous value investor Benjamin Graham, is a fickle individual.  When shopping for potential investments, I occasionally get access to the attractive price, which is what happened with my investment in WEC Energy (NYSE: WEC).  The yield, the history of dividend growth, and the opportunity presented by the utility's ongoing shift toward cleaner energy was more than enough to get me in the door.
